@startuml
title CircleGuard - Publisher Subscriber con Kafka

actor Student
participant "form-service" as Form
participant Kafka
participant "promotion-service" as Promotion
participant "notification-service" as Notification

Student -> Form : submitSurvey()
Form -> Kafka : publish survey.submitted
Kafka -> Promotion : consume survey.submitted
Promotion -> Kafka : publish certificate.validated
Promotion -> Kafka : publish promotion.status.changed
Promotion -> Kafka : publish alert.priority
Promotion -> Kafka : publish circle.fenced
Kafka -> Notification : consume promotion.status.changed
Kafka -> Notification : consume alert.priority
Kafka -> Notification : consume circle.fenced

note over Kafka
Los eventos de auditoria (audit.identity.accessed y notification.audit)
existen en el sistema, pero se omiten aqui para enfocar el flujo de negocio.
end note

@enduml